Simplifies choosing your next Leetcode data-structure and algorithm question.

Utilize AI to help you select your next data structures and algorithms problem based on a machine learning model that adjusts to your skill level as you use it.

 This extension enables you to increase productivity when studying for Data structures and algorithms leaving the guesswork out by providing you with the hard choice of selecting a question.

Instruction to use are as followed: 
- Complete starter question 
- Rate the difficulty on a scale 
- Congrats, you got a new question that better fits your skill level.

The more you use it, the more accurate it gets. The extension will improve productivity so you can prepare for your upcoming interview. Download today and work smarter.
